---
layout: base
title: Newsletter
description: Subscribe to The Traveling Times newsletter.
permalink: /newsletter/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-16); padding-bottom: var(--space-24);">

  {# ── Hero ── #}
  <header style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-16); text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-3xl); line-height: var(--leading-tight); margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">The newsletter. Direct to your inbox.</h1>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">
      New articles about travel, poetry, entertainment, fashion, art, music, and dance — delivered when they are published. No spam, no algorithms.
    </p>
  </header>

  {# ── Sign-up form ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-20);">
    <form class="subscribe-form subscribe-form--stacked" novalidate>
      <label for="subscribe-email-newsletter" class="visually-hidden">Your email address</label>
      <input
        class="subscribe-form__input"
        id="subscribe-email-newsletter"
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="your@email.com"
        autocomplete="email"
        required>
      <button class="subscribe-form__btn" type="submit">Subscribe — it's free</button>
    </form>
    <div class="subscribe-status" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></div>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-ink-faint); text-align: center; margin-top: var(--space-4); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
      Free, always. Unsubscribe at any time. We don't share your address. <a href="/privacy/" style="color: var(--color-ink-faint);">Privacy policy.</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  {# ── What you get ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);">
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">What to expect</h2>
    <dl style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-8);">
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">One email per article</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">Each email carries one piece — fully readable in your inbox.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Every topic</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">Travel, poetry, entertainment, fashion, art, music, dance — whatever is published, you will receive it.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">No tracking</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">Open tracking and click tracking are disabled. We do not monitor your reading behaviour inside the email.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  {# ── Other ways to follow ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">Other ways to follow</h2>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-4);">
      <a href="/feed.xml" style="display: block; padding: var(--space-5); border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink);">
        <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">RSS Feed</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">Subscribe in any RSS reader.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/reading-list/" style="display: block; padding: var(--space-5); border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink);">
        <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Reading List</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">Bookmark articles to read later.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
